  "prompt": "Which is the best brand of whisky in India?",
  "response": "Determining the \"best\" brand of whisky can be subjective, as it often depends on personal preferences such as taste, budget, and occasion. However, here are some popular and well-regarded whisky brands in India:\n\n1. **Amrut**: Amrut is known for its high-quality single malt whiskies and has gained international acclaim for its products.\n\n2. **Paul John**: Another Indian brand that has received international recognition, Paul John offers a range of single malt whiskies that are highly regarded.\n\n3. **Rampur**: Rampur Distillery offers premium Indian single malt whisky and is known for its smoothness and rich flavor.\n\n4. **Officer\u2019s Choice**: Popular in India, Officer's Choice is one of the highest-selling brands, known for its affordability and accessibility.\n\n5. **Royal Stag**: Known for its blend of Indian grain spirits and imported Scotch malts, Royal Stag is widely consumed in India.\n\n6. **McDowell\u2019s No.1**: McDowell's is a leading brand famous for its variety of whiskies that cater to different segments of the market.\n\nThese brands are known for their quality and consumer satisfaction, but it is always a good idea to try a few different ones to determine your own favorite.",
